From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: WebKitGTKWin Port <webkitgtkwin@local>
Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] WebKitGTKWin: stage Windows font private headers

The Windows Cairo font backend exposes FontMemoryResource through
FontPlatformData.h, together with the SharedGDIObject helper. Stage those
helpers as WebCore private headers so WebKit sources can include
FontPlatformData.h from the copied private header directory.
---
--- a/Source/WebCore/PlatformGTK.cmake
+++ b/Source/WebCore/PlatformGTK.cmake
@@ -35,6 +35,11 @@
             platform/win/WebCoreInstanceHandle.cpp
         )
 
+        list(APPEND WebCore_PRIVATE_FRAMEWORK_HEADERS
+            platform/graphics/opentype/FontMemoryResource.h
+            platform/graphics/win/SharedGDIObject.h
+        )
+
         list(APPEND WebCore_LIBRARIES
             dwrite
             gdi32
